title: iPhone Q1 2016 Sales Estimates Apple Inc.s Smartphone Sales May Decline For First Time Says Analyst

iPhone Q1 2016 Sales Estimates: Apple Inc.'s Smartphone Sales May Decline For First Time, Says Analyst 
IBTimes Friday 23rd October, 2015 
The iPhone 6S could be Apple's first flagship?smartphone that fails to outdo its predecessor. In Apple Inc.'s report for the October-December quarter, KGI Securities analyst Ming-Chi Kuo forecasts iPhone sales to come in between 70 million and 75 million units, according to a research note obtained by...
